-- Strict tradition: only the 15 unconditionally valid moods.
-- No existential import, no subaltern moods.

tradition Strict

proof Barbara
  Every M is P
  Every S is M
  ∴ Every S is P

proof Celarent
  No M is P
  Every S is M
  ∴ No S is P

proof Cesare
  No P is M
  Every S is M
  ∴ No S is P

proof Baroco
  Every P is M
  Some S is not M
  ∴ Some S is not P

proof Bocardo
  Some M is not P
  Every M is S
  ∴ Some S is not P
